。","career":["seiyu"],"id":21163,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":203241},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/6e/16/204322_crt_bZEcs.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/6e/16/204322_crt_bZEcs.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/6e/16/204322_crt_bZEcs.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/6e/16/204322_crt_bZEcs.jpg"},"name":"白魔法使い","summary":"","relation":"配角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/bc/f9/4645_prsn_h3TZT.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/bc/f9/4645_prsn_h3TZT.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/bc/f9/4645_prsn_h3TZT.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/bc/f9/4645_prsn_h3TZT.jpg"},"name":"立花慎之介","short_summary":"日本男性声优，出身于岐阜县。过去曾隶属于Production baobab，2011年6月1日移籍于AXL ONE，并于2018年3月31日离开，移籍到与福山润一同创立的BLACK SHIP。\r\n\r\n“立花慎之介”为艺名，本姓是与“立花”同音的“橘”（第40弹おまえらのためだろ!），原名是“橘秀宣”（たちばなひでのり）。\r\n儿时看动画幸运女神，而立志成为声优。\r\n声音透明且清爽，常常负责少年与青年角色的配音。\r\n与成濑诚组成音乐团体Lux-age；其后与日野聪组成ELEKITER ROUND φ。\r\n在进入配音行业之前从事了4年左右的默剧与日本舞踊（深水流）演出。\r\n与福山润、菅沼久义、日野聪、小野大辅、间岛淳司以及近藤孝行同年出生，并组成DABA。\r\n喜爱城堡，在熊本城修复之际因捐款之由名字被记在了天守阁。\r\n喜爱玩Battle Spirits，还经常在其日志谈及游戏相关的话题。\r\n家里养了一只叫Lily的挪威森林猫。\r\n2013年以漫画原作家身份出道，出道作是“箱庭の令嬢探侦”，于杂志YOUNG ACE连载，其后更亲自编写了小说版。\r\n2017年1月5日宣布已于1月1日跟声优高梁碧结婚。","career":["writer","artist","seiyu"],"id":4645,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":204322},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/5e/b1/205190_crt_223CE.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/5e/b1/205190_crt_223CE.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/5e/b1/205190_crt_223CE.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/5e/b1/205190_crt_223CE.jpg"},"name":"マクシミリアン","summary":"","relation":"配角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/de/86/31434_prsn_7ull7.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/de/86/31434_prsn_7ull7.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/de/86/31434_prsn_7ull7.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/de/86/31434_prsn_7ull7.jpg"},"name":"坂泰斗","short_summary":"坂 泰斗は、日本の男性声優。福岡県出身。大沢事務所所属。\r\n\r\n略歴\r\n\r\n福岡県で生まれ、茨城県で育つ。父の仕事の関係でメキシコに住んでいた時期があり、帰国子女である。\r\n\r\n昔は職業としての声優は無知で、アニメも見ていなかった。帰国後の高校2年生ぐらいにアニメを見始めて、「こんな職業あるんだ、やってみよう」と声優を目指した。高校の頃に見ていたアニメは『けいおん!』。\r\n\r\nプロ・フィット声優養成所卒業。2017年4月よりプロ・フィット所属して、声優としての活動を始める。2019年4月1日より事務所預かりから準所属。2022年1月1日、プロ・フィットが同年3月末で閉鎖することに伴い、大沢事務所へ移籍。\r\n\r\nゲーム『メモリーズオフ -Innocent Fille-』の楠瀬累役で初主人公を務める。","career":["seiyu"],"id":31434,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":205190}],"detail":[{"birth_mon":null,"gender":"male","birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/2b/6d/198637_crt_qhS7p.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/2b/6d/198637_crt_qhS7p.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/2b/6d/198637_crt_qhS7p.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/2b/6d/198637_crt_qhS7p.jpg"},"summary":"","name":"焔の魔法使い","infobox":[{"key":"简体中文名","value":"焰之魔法师"},{"key":"别名","value":[]},{"key":"性别","value":"男"}],"stat":{"comments":0,"collects":0},"id":198637,"locked":false,"type":1,"nsfw":false},{"birth_mon":null,"gender":"male","birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/af/86/201164_crt_pKKWK.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/af/86/201164_crt_pKKWK.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/af/86/201164_crt_pKKWK.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/af/86/201164_crt_pKKWK.jpg"},"summary":"","name":"ネズミの魔法使い","infobox":[{"key":"简体中文名","value":"鼠之魔法师"},{"key":"别名","value":[]},{"key":"性别","value":"男"}],"stat":{"comments":0,"collects":0},"id":201164,"locked":false,"type":1,"nsfw":false},{"birth_mon":null,"gender":null,"birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/01/e9/197883_crt_TBW0e.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/01/e9/197883_crt_TBW0e.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/01/e9/197883_crt_TBW0e.jpg","medium":"https://lain